84
00:03:40,899 --> 00:03:44,979
Chapter three, four, and five provide us for a record

85
00:03:44,979 --> 00:03:46,619
not only of those that were there

86
00:03:46,619 --> 00:03:48,619
in chapter number three extensively,

87
00:03:49,460 --> 00:03:50,740
