127
00:05:32,660 --> 00:05:34,179
I believe that as we look here

128
00:05:34,179 --> 00:05:35,540
at this passage of Scripture,

129
00:05:35,540 --> 00:05:36,980
there's some things that we need to learn

130
00:05:36,980 --> 00:05:38,540
if you're taking notes, number one,

131
00:05:38,540 --> 00:05:41,579
