132
00:05:41,579 --> 00:05:43,660
We need to learn to recognize the enemy.

133
00:05:43,700 --> 00:05:45,739
Now understand that by this time,

134
00:05:45,739 --> 00:05:47,339
I mean, Nehemiah had been working

