00:06:14,779 --> 00:06:18,339
And so Nehemiah at this particular time of his ministry,

150
00:06:18,339 --> 00:06:22,380
he was able to easily identify who his enemies were.

151
00:06:23,459 --> 00:06:24,899
But I want you to understand

152
00:06:26,140 --> 00:06:28,839
that though the opposition to the work of God

153
00:06:28,839 --> 00:06:30,700
began immediately,

154
00:06:30,700 --> 00:06:34,059
I find that as I read Nehemiah chapter number six,

155
00:06:34,059 --> 00:06:36,420
that we discover that the enemy

