00:06:49,540 --> 00:06:51,339
and all of the things that they said.

163
00:06:51,339 --> 00:06:52,899
But now in chapter number six,

164
00:06:52,899 --> 00:06:57,779
the level of deception increases exponentially.

165
00:06:57,779 --> 00:06:59,420
