166
00:06:59,420 --> 00:07:01,459
through chapter number six this morning

167
00:07:01,459 --> 00:07:04,079
that we find that Nehemiah was able

168
00:07:04,079 --> 00:07:07,019
to consistently recognize the enemy.

169
00:07:07,019 --> 00:07:08,140
Can I tell you this morning

170
00:07:08,179 --> 00:07:09,660
that the enemy doesn't always show up

171
00:07:09,660 --> 00:07:11,179
by saying, I'm your enemy.

172
00:07:12,739 --> 00:07:14,660
In fact, it's very rare

173
00:07:14,660 --> 00:07:18,700
that an enemy would show up that way, right?

174
00:07:18,700 --> 00:07:20,920
And so we find that as we look at this passage of Scripture

175
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:22,839
that the deception is increasing.

176
00:07:22,839 --> 00:07:24,540
Remember what the word of God says

177
00:07:24,540 --> 00:07:27,059
in the book of Ephesians in chapter number six,

178
00:07:27,059 --> 00:07:31,380
and we studied this book a few years ago in its entirety,

179
00:07:31,380 --> 00:07:33,220
but we find in Ephesians chapter number six

180
00:07:33,220 --> 00:07:34,859
in verse number 10,

181
00:07:34,859 --> 00:07:36,739
Paul says this to the believers in Ephesus,

182
00:07:36,739 --> 00:07:38,140
finally, my brethren,

183
00:07:38,140 --> 00:07:41,260
be strong in the Lord and the power of His might.

184
00:07:41,260 --> 00:07:43,420
Put on the whole armor of God

185
00:07:43,420 --> 00:07:45,420
that you may be able to stand

186
00:07:45,420 --> 00:07:49,700
against the wiles of the devil.

187
00:07:49,700 --> 00:07:51,980
That word wiles, it carries with it

188
00:07:51,980 --> 00:07:56,980
the idea of deceit, deception, craftiness, tricky.

189
00:07:57,980 --> 00:08:00,299
Remember that it says of the serpent

190
00:08:00,299 --> 00:08:01,839
in Genesis chapter number three,

191
00:08:01,839 --> 00:08:05,779
that he was more subtle than any beast of the field.

192
00:08:05,779 --> 00:08:07,420
We find that it's in verse number 12

193
00:08:07,420 --> 00:08:09,260
of the same passage in Ephesians six

194
00:08:09,260 --> 00:08:13,500
that Paul says that we wrestle not against flesh and blood,

195
00:08:13,500 --> 00:08:15,619
but against principalities, against powers,

196
00:08:15,619 --> 00:08:17,980
against the rulers of the darkness of this world,

197
00:08:17,980 --> 00:08:22,600
against spiritual wickedness in high places.

198
00:08:23,619 --> 00:08:27,140
I believe that as we look here in Nehemiah chapter number six

199
00:08:27,140 --> 00:08:30,859
it reminds me as we think about the deception increasing

200
00:08:30,859 --> 00:08:32,580
and we think about the attacks

