00:08:35,780 --> 00:08:39,239
it reminds me of what we read back in the book of Numbers

204
00:08:39,239 --> 00:08:40,960
under the counsel of Balaam.

205
00:08:40,960 --> 00:08:45,039
Remember that Balaam could not curse the people of God.

206
00:08:45,039 --> 00:08:46,960
Though Balak wanted him to,

207
00:08:46,960 --> 00:08:49,820
we find that it was through the counsel of Balaam

208
00:08:49,820 --> 00:08:53,960
that he encouraged the people of God to corrupt themselves.

209
00:08:53,960 --> 00:08:57,539
You can read that in Numbers 31 and verse number 16.

210
00:08:57,539 --> 00:09:00,840
We also find that it's very similar to what you read of

211
00:09:00,840 --> 00:09:03,280
in the book of Joshua in the ninth chapter

212
00:09:03,280 --> 00:09:06,159
with the deception of the Gibeonites.

213
00:09:06,159 --> 00:09:09,659
And we find that our enemy is going to consistently

214
00:09:09,659 --> 00:09:12,599
and regularly increase the deception

215
00:09:12,599 --> 00:09:14,760
because he's our enemy.

216
00:09:16,679 --> 00:09:19,520
Understand as we look at this point this morning

217
00:09:19,520 --> 00:09:21,679
that we need to learn to recognize the enemy,

218
00:09:21,679 --> 00:09:24,880
we need to understand the objective of the enemy.

219
00:09:24,880 --> 00:09:29,159
I mean, ultimately their objective is to destroy the work.

220
00:09:29,159 --> 00:09:31,119
And that's what they'd like to do.

221
00:09:31,119 --> 00:09:35,400
But I believe that the enemy, though he understands,

222
00:09:35,400 --> 00:09:38,440
and we'll look at some promises at the end of the message

223
00:09:38,440 --> 00:09:41,880
this morning, the work of God will march on.

224
00:09:41,880 --> 00:09:46,099
I believe that where he finds great satisfaction

225
00:09:46,099 --> 00:09:48,640
is in hindering the work of God.

226
00:09:50,119 --> 00:09:52,299
Hindering the work of God.

227
00:09:52,299 --> 00:09:54,559
That's exactly what the enemy had been trying to do

228
00:09:54,559 --> 00:09:56,080
in chapters four and five.

229
00:09:56,080 --> 00:09:58,039
And now in chapter number six,

230
00:09:58,039 --> 00:10:00,119
we find that the enemy recognizes

231
00:10:00,119 --> 00:10:02,539
that the building is continuing to go on.

232
00:10:02,539 --> 00:10:04,159
I mean, the wall is near completion.

233
00:10:04,159 --> 00:10:08,539
It says that the doors had not yet been set up upon the gates,

234
00:10:08,539 --> 00:10:10,719
but we find that they're nearing completion.

235
00:10:10,719 --> 00:10:13,799
And so the enemy is going to elevate and increase

236
00:10:13,799 --> 00:10:15,119
the level of deception.

237
00:10:15,119 --> 00:10:18,279
And they're going to come and try to hinder the work.

238
00:10:18,279 --> 00:10:19,599
So what do they do?

239
00:10:19,599 --> 00:10:21,279
We understand what their objective is,

240
00:10:21,279 --> 00:10:24,679
but look at what the method is that's employed in Nehemiah

241
00:10:24,679 --> 00:10:25,759
chapter number 6.

242
00:10:25,759 --> 00:10:27,719
First, we find in verses 2 through 4

243
00:10:27,719 --> 00:10:32,279
that there is a request for a meeting in one of the villages.

244
00:10:32,279 --> 00:10:34,679
The Bible says in verse number 2,

245
00:10:34,679 --> 00:10:37,559
come let us meet together in some one of the villages

246
00:10:37,559 --> 00:10:39,559
in the plain of Ono.

247
00:10:39,559 --> 00:10:44,159
Notice what Nehemiah says, but they thought to do me mischief.

248
00:10:44,159 --> 00:10:47,519
And so they desired to have this meeting.

249
00:10:47,519 --> 00:10:51,039
No doubt, I believe that if this meeting would have taken place,

250
00:10:51,039 --> 00:10:54,039
they would have sought to intimidate Nehemiah

251
00:10:54,039 --> 00:10:55,479
from continuing with the work.

252
00:10:55,519 --> 00:10:59,239
I believe that really another plan of these individuals

253
00:10:59,239 --> 00:11:02,119
was to get Nehemiah distracted from the work,

254
00:11:02,119 --> 00:11:03,959
remove him from the work he was doing.

255
00:11:03,959 --> 00:11:05,799
Notice what he says in verse number 3,

256
00:11:05,799 --> 00:11:07,639
and I sent messengers unto them saying,

257
00:11:07,639 --> 00:11:12,439
I am doing a great work so that I cannot come down.

258
00:11:12,439 --> 00:11:18,919
Why should the work cease whilst I leave it and come down to you?

259
00:11:18,919 --> 00:11:20,959
See, the enemy wants the work to cease.

260
00:11:20,959 --> 00:11:22,479
He wants to hinder the work.

